Well, I updated quite a few things from the original power. Here is a quick list:
  • Fixes texture alignment in places
  • Optimized the pillars
  • Fixed some lighting bugs
  • Fixed the custom box texture
  • Fixed misaligned support beam
  • Players now spawn with deagle
  • Minor frame rate improvements
  • Many small other tweaks
Thank you Ruff and hacksawjack for the custom logos. To the ggn members that tested this, be sure to remove the file you have because it differs from the file I have. Thanks! Thank you to the people at GGN who gave me constructive criticism.
